      "$value": "Haas Grotesk Display R Web",
      "$type": "fontFamily",
      "$description": "All UI text: navigation links, body copy, footer, labels. The 14px weight 400 is the default for everything clickable; 20px weight 500 for subheadings and journal titles. This is the working typeface — small, neutral, Swiss-grid functional."
    },
