      "$value": "Yinka Sans Ultra",
      "$type": "fontFamily",
      "$description": "Exclusive to the studio wordmark and oversized display moments. The +0.04em tracking at 120px is critical — it gives the dense letterforms air without losing the custom geometric character. Custom face only used at this display scale; never below 80px."
